`Mockito.when(something.isCalled()).thenReturn(something);` `something` needs to be a mock, in your case, it&#39;s not, **tested** is an instance of `CalculateDateService`. You can read more about @Mock and @InjectMocks [here](https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/difference-between-mock-and-injectmocks-in-mockito/).

